Olaf Pooley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olaf_Pooley 0 Olaf Pooley (13 March 1914 – 14 July 2015) was an English actor and writer, best known for his role as Professor Stahlman in the 1970 Doctor Who serial Inferno.
